      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_23_1380-1428",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "1380-1428",
      "markText": "第4章.利用最小上界的两条性质：集合中的每一个数都不可能大于它，任何小于它的数都不是集合的上界。",
      "totalCount": 2192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1380&rangeEnd=1428",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1380&rangeEnd=1428"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_15_37422-37865",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "37422-37865",
      "markText": "如果E是紧集，那么由定理11.7可知，E是中的闭集，而根据定理11.10, E也是中的有界集。",
      "totalCount": 2188,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=37422&rangeEnd=37865",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=37422&rangeEnd=37865"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_23_4761-4779",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "4761-4779",
      "markText": "第17章.不要害怕取子序列的子序列！",
      "totalCount": 2166,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4761&rangeEnd=4779",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4761&rangeEnd=4779"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_3_9326-9361",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9326-9361",
      "markText": "海涅–博雷尔定理是实分析的中心结果之一，特别是关于紧集理论的中心结果。",
      "totalCount": 1939,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9326&rangeEnd=9361",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9326&rangeEnd=9361"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_23_3775-4304",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "3775-4304",
      "markText": "第15章.你可以像归纳证明那样去构造一个特定的子序列：定义，然后假设某结论对成立，并证明该结论对也成立。",
      "totalCount": 1879,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3775&rangeEnd=4304",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3775&rangeEnd=4304"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_11_15534-15856",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "15534-15856",
      "markText": "对于任意两个集合A和B，如果，那么A和B要么是元素个数相同的有限集，要么都是可数集，要么都是不可数集。",
      "totalCount": 1797,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=15534&rangeEnd=15856",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=15534&rangeEnd=15856"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_5_9600-9953",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9600-9953",
      "markText": "命题1.如果，那么n属于。",
      "totalCount": 1678,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9600&rangeEnd=9953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9600&rangeEnd=9953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_23_5486-5561",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "5486-5561",
      "markText": "所以你可以把你所知道的关于序列的所有知识都应用到级数中，另外级数还有比较判别法（参见定理19.5和定理19.6）和柯西凝聚判别法（参见定理19.9）。",
      "totalCount": 1331,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5486&rangeEnd=5561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5486&rangeEnd=5561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153888_5_32493-32550",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "32493-32550",
      "markText": "数学归纳法就像多米诺骨牌一样：如果我们把所有的多米诺骨牌都摆好，然后只撞倒第一张骨牌，那么其余所有的骨牌都会倒下。",
      "totalCount": 1126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153888&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=32493&rangeEnd=32550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bfd32d90813aba29cg018846?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=32493&rangeEnd=32550"
    },
    {
